{"title":"京剧现代戏人物赞","authors":["陈今言　秦嘉"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":7,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"京剧现代戏人物赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《杜鹃山》〔北京京剧团演出〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《红色娘子军》〔中国京剧院四团演出〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈今言画　秦嘉诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌豆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横冲直闯不畏难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三起三落放眼看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此红旗永不倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜鹃山接井冈山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴琼花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挣断锁镣上战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪痕抛尽气昂扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养成一片大无畏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火中飞腾金凤凰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}